name: Spectre - Forest - Video Short
description:
Spectre saying hello :D

Info:
Spectres origin is unknown. They have been traveling through space and time before those concepts were even conceived. With their trusty sprite "Glitch" a hybrid mechanical organic being from Zeta Terra 3, they travel together exploring, observing and documenting.

This piece is the introduction to the series. It will explore different locations, scenery and various styles of art.

I hope you enjoy and I really look forward to creating this series for you :]
